eba3f8dcf118297df","tid":1121510,"uid":40133,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:00:51.000Z","msg":"屋企人有認知障礙症的話真係要睇緊啲<br />\n最好畀手帶佢戴住，寫上老人家既名同聯絡人既電話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果唔見咗真係唔知邊度搵<br />\n<br />\n利申，係地鐵站見過一個阿婆迷咗路，以為自己仲係三十歲<br />\n好在佢有電話係身，即刻搵地鐵職員幫手聯絡屋企人<br />\n屋企人黎到勁唔耐煩，係度話個老人家<br />\n我就解釋一輪畀佢聽應該點做，但佢就唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再利申 護狗"},{"pid":"097ae1e5ea9baa09a17a76bf2ae36ec513a9d260","tid":1121510,"uid":40133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:01:40.000Z","msg":"唔記得講<br />\n希望樓主快啲搵到婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721b292ad59e1543aca1bcc078e68367ed80da3e","tid":1121510,"uid":111444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"唔係附近<br />\n希望老人家可以快啲搵得返"},{"pid":"1ed71e78bb7024b6390fda40c008e7c4795f4ba0","tid":1121510,"uid":183145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:06:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fff51e7059f2786641a8dfb8b2f9ad5dd443c451","tid":1121510,"uid":203696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:07:23.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"085109ed55c434ae930cdd139c28a3dee85f45e5","tid":1121510,"uid":128325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:07:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c364692945af3cd0d2504e8c1716f67fe6775bf","tid":1121510,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:08:48.000Z","msg":"推 祝早日搵到婆婆"},{"pid":"4ad18a7e8579f2428349b94b4770e49801169750","tid":1121510,"uid":67931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:12:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e5ae6d30f0e8ce777e0aeefc81b147a41ec4682","tid":1121510,"uid":236732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:14:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b09b1873aece11b0